sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    title Material Upload and Indexing Flow

    actor Student
    participant Web as Web App
    participant Storage as Firebase Storage
    participant API as Cloud Functions
    participant DB as Firestore

    Student->>Web: Upload material
    Web->>Storage: Upload raw file
    Web->>API: POST /materialIndex

    API->>Storage: Download file
    API->>API: Extract text and build chunks
    API->>DB: Save material metadata + chunks
    DB-->>Web: Material status update
    Web-->>Student: Material ready for chat
